skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: city attractions
des:
City attractions will help you find attractions around the world

After you have enabled the service, you just have to say "Alexa, ask city attractions" and you can get started.

or try saying things like
- Alexa, ask city attractions to find attractions in chicago
- Alexa, ask city attractions for san francisco attractions
- Alexa, ask city attractions for london attractions

You can also say " Alexa, ask city attractions for help"
